{"tid":2008822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再怪達粉OK?","createTime":"2020-05-09T09:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T06:15:54.000Z","uid":227275,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b18b317edaec5cb411374ca84f505b7dcf60e47","tid":2008822,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"班毒撚由細到大都冇朋友 又冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每晚都要靠達狗直播黎做免費娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達狗又成日叫班觀眾做兄弟兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到班傻仔又真係當左達狗係兄弟 事實上只係生財工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知上年6月果時連登仔又逼到達狗發晒癲露正面目  爆晒粗話人引戰狗 又唔開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到班達粉 無左精神支柱 失晒控  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎鷹kmdd郭大俠以前既達狗真兄弟都反達狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而達粉就好似乞兒咁去達狗FB IG 留言問幾時開返台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n達粉以為自己真係達狗兄弟 係既 不過達狗份人專門吞兄食弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699431ceb105892dd3eda479662c91a675f0ff25","tid":2008822,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"達狗正仆街 BLOCKED"},{"pid":"2c89698f14b8c7c8495a79e4eb5a67ac01289f49","tid":2008822,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"699431ceb105892dd3eda479662c91a675f0ff25","tid":2008822,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"達狗正仆街 BLOCKED"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcad6f6ab1e8a821b0938ff941846c9f6a03be8b","tid":2008822,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/